---[Verse:1]---
Praise to the Lord
the Almighty
The King of creation
---[Verse:1]---
O my soul praise Him
For He is thy health
and salvation
---[Verse:1]---
All ye who hear
Now to His temple
draw near
Join me in glad adoration
---[Verse:2]---
Praise to the Lord
Who o'er all things
So wondrously reigneth
---[Verse:2]---
Shelters thee under His wings
Yes so gently sustaineth
---[Verse:2]---
Hast Thou not seen
How all thy longings have been
Granted in what He ordaineth
---[Verse:3]---
Praise to the Lord
O let all that is
in me adore Him
---[Verse:3]---
All that hath life and breath
Come now with praises
before Him
---[Verse:3]---
Let the amen sound from
His people again
Gladly for aye we adore Him
---[Verse:4]---
Praise to the Lord
Who doth prosper
Thy work and defend thee
---[Verse:4]---
Surely His goodness and mercy
Here daily attend thee
---[Verse:4]---
Ponder anew
what the Almighty can do
If with His love He befriend thee
